<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-03-25T14:16:46-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-03-25T14:16:46-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-25T14:16:46-04:00</updated><title> Meta 的新选择退出设置限制了 Instagram 和 Threads 上政治的可见性</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Threads 应用程序徽标插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/_T1nEWsTQTNm2i5mR8qb9pVePCw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/73232065/STK156_Instagram_threads_2.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;c4fozU&quot;>;Meta 的高管已经说过一段时间了，他们&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/9/24067742/instagram-threads-meta-political-content-recommished-feeds&quot;>;不想在以下位置增加有关政治的帖子&lt;/a>;他们的应用程序。现在，Instagram 和 Threads 中添加了限制“政治内容”推荐的选择退出设置。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;c9jTyb&quot;>;您可以在 Instagram 的“内容偏好设置”帐户设置下找到它。从那里，默认启用“限制您不关注的人的政治内容”。该设置也适用于 Threads，因为该应用与 Instagram 共享其帐户系统。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;NCuo7w&quot;>;Meta 认为这一新设置有利于用户选择，但该公司表示事实并非如此限制人们选择关注的帐户中的政治内容的范围。虽然这一变化&lt;a href=&quot;https://about.instagram.com/blog/announcements/continuing-our-approach-to-political-content-on-instagram-and-threads&quot;>;于二月初首次宣布&lt; /a>;，Meta 发言人安迪...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/25/24111604/meta-setting-downranks-politics-instagram-线程&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/25/24111604/meta-setting-downranks-politics-instagram-threads" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/25/24111604/meta-setting-downranks-politics-instagram-threads</id><author><name>亚历克斯·希思</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-25T12:57:44-04:00</published><updated> 20